{
  "stem": "9486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Tell me all your brothers names and your sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mine older-- my oldest-- my sister is Goldie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older brother is [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Label. ?] The-- the third brother, Meir.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was Edna, and then Moshe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, mine older brother was a little troublemaker, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Used to go all the trees, cutting the apples, and very-- very talent boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the Meir was a very quiet boy, shy boy, very talent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Israel, when he-- he was-- he was a-- he taught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Paper, he taught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- that he wrote a paper for the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Moshe is very talent, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anything what you going in in his house is he made.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The first time when I brought him here-- my sister, my brother to my daughter's wedding-- he liked so much my house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He liked the wood, and he liked the [? chandelier. ?] Two years later, I came to visit him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He did over his house the same like mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he did it alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He's very talent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's right-- he was-- he finishes work, [? event ?] retiring very early.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the army didn't give him to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They call him back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he's now is teaching in the school children, what are very low.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, they are on top.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- they don't want to be in the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he's a teacher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Like, [INAUDIBLE] hand, when he's going out, a boy, he's already good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everybody didn't believe it, we're going to have to leave-- leave the house to run away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought we're going go away someplace under the mountains, under the water, some, to be over the night and we would come back.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
